GDG on Campus NEHU Team‬"><div class="x1c4vz4f x3nfvp2 xuce83p x1bft6iq x1i7k8ik xq9mrsl x6s0dn4"><div class="x78zum5"><span dir="auto" class="x1rg5ohu _ao3e" style="min-height: 0px;">DibakarPatar</span></div></div><span>:&nbsp;</span><span dir="ltr" class="x1iyjqo2 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6 xlyipyv xuxw1ft x1rg5ohu _ao3e" style="min-height: 0px;">Dear members,

We have noticed that some individuals are attempting to promote or sell courses within the community. To maintain the purpose and trust of this community, promotions or sales of courses are not allowed unless they are officially approved by the admin team.

Please be cautious of unsolicited course promotions or messages that promise quick results or special offers, as not all of them may be genuine.

This community is meant for learning, collaboration, and sharing reliable resources. We request everyone to respect this guideline and help keep this space safe and valuable for all members.

